{
  "chapter": 25,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十五回 两异叟。原思敏以七孔笛吹奏催眠曲，与兄长原思聪合力催眠七情魔。芮玮以龟息大功抵御笛音，随后以大愚剑一招击败原思敏，逼迫原氏兄弟救醒七情魔。七情魔醒来后，温笑透露一灯神尼怀抱绝美女子的消息，芮玮追问女子容貌，赵柔正要描述时，聋哑二老突然现身追杀赵柔。七情魔誓死维护兄弟，双方激烈对峙。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "温笑，你也坐下罢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二弟的笛音天下无双，你们好好听，莫要错过机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "风摇荡，雨潆潆，翠条柔弱花头重，春衫窄，香肌湿，记得年时，共摘莲子。都如梦，何曾共？可怜孤似钗头风。关山绝，晚云碧，燕儿来也，又无消息！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "温笑呀！温笑呀！你虽然闭下眼睛，却不曾塞住耳朵，岂知老夫兄弟俩不用视觉，利用听觉亦可教尔等中术！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "未必见得，在下芮玮便未中术。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你……你……怎会没睡去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "凭仗邪术胜人，卑鄙下流！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你敢对我再说卑鄙下流？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "有何不敢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "你就是再多十只眼睛，我也不会中术！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "大哥……他……怎么不怕催眠术？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "我也不知！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "你们有本领在真功夫上战胜他们，利用邪术得胜，岂非卑鄙下流已极？这样你们纵然战胜一万次，天下亦无人认为胜得公平！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不管公平不公平，老夫这时就有夺取七情魔性命的能力，他们会有吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "他们虽无，你们亦无夺取他们性命的能力。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你的意思，咱们要取他们的性命时，你要阻拦？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "正是这个意思！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小子凭恃什么，说此大话？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "就凭这个！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "一柄木剑，何足为奇？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你以这只木剑能够击碎阿罗逸多的肩骨，这剑上功夫确实了得。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "但在咱们看来，微末之技。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "在下就以微末之技向阁下讨教。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你要败了如何？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "任凭处置！但若在下胜了又如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你要如何！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "就请将七情魔完全救转，不可令他们有一点伤害。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你与七情魔有什么关系？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "一点关系也没有！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "想不到小子竟敢在咱们兄弟面前抱不平，未免太不自量力，小子出招！老夫一人接着。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "二弟，可要留神一点，不要大意。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "要战快将兵刃取出。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "与你过招还要兵刃？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "阁下要空手接招？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "老夫过的桥比你走的路还多，空手接招又有何妨，小子不要多说，快出招吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "你要空手接招，在下一招内胜你！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "放屁！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "二弟怎么了？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "还……还好，他手下留情，没有将我腿骨拍碎……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你已胜了，还要如何？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "说话不算数吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你今日战胜我二弟，自怪他学艺不精也还罢了，但一定要我施救七情魔，这样的事咱们兄弟就永不会忘记了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "别威胁，芮某只知胜了，你就得救好七情魔，尔后有什么不了的事，尽管记下，我可不在乎。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "咱们兄弟虽不是你的敌手，但总有人能制住你，那时落在咱们手上，可别怪心黑手辣。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "咱们与七情魔的仇恨不是三言两语解说得开的，好不容易令他们落在咱们手中，以雪当年之恨，你定要强自出头，我看不值得吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "有什么大不了的事，不过是彼此间好胜心而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "可没那么简单。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "是你自个说的，一时意气用事将七情魔打伤，如今他们来寻仇，不幸又败，这不是为了好胜心吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "七情魔不是好相与的人，否则也不会称之为魔，当年无冤无故，你想咱们会凭意气用事将他们打伤？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "不是为了好胜心，那为何故？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不能跟你说！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "不说罢了，但言而不可无信，快将七情魔救转过来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好，我救就是！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "等他们醒来再走不迟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你信不过我吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "好！我相信七情魔已被救好，你们走吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "凡事皆因强出头，到时招得祸满身……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮兄，原氏兄弟呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "他们走了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_rou",
      "speaker_name": "赵柔",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他们真走了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhao_rou",
      "text": "真走了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bei",
      "speaker_name": "莫悲",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不信他们就这样轻易放过咱们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_han",
      "speaker_name": "钟寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这……不可能呀……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "没有什么不可能，定是咱们昏倒后，芮兄在他兄弟俩的手中救了咱们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮兄大德，小弟永不忘怀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_fen",
      "speaker_name": "吴愤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你会在原氏兄弟手中救了我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_hen",
      "speaker_name": "葛恨",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我才不相信，他有能耐在原氏兄弟手中救了咱们！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ge_hen",
      "text": "不信算了，我芮玮并没叫你相信曾经救了你们！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "六弟无知，芮兄不要见怪，咱们心照不宣但芮兄是个大有能耐的人物，小弟是知道的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "我有什么能耐，不过粗识拳脚而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮兄客气了……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "你们怎会与原氏兄弟结仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "没有啊！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "仅因武功上一点胜负，彼此不服而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chi",
      "text": "我不信，到底其中有何情由？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_fen",
      "speaker_name": "吴愤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不信拉倒！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "一灯神尼说……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "她说什么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "昨日午间咱们遇见一灯神尼时，见她怀中抱着一个绝美的女子……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chi",
      "speaker_name": "章痴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那女子的美貌，实是章某生平绝未见过，教我才见一面，已深深爱上……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_rou",
      "speaker_name": "赵柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当我见时，食欲大动，有云：秀色可餐。妙啊！妙啊！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhao_rou",
      "text": "那……那……女子……可是长的瓜子脸吗？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我没看清，让我想想……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_rou",
      "speaker_name": "赵柔",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我看清了！我看清了！她长得像……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "聋子",
      "listener": "char_zhao_rou",
      "text": "王八羔子，你在这里，总算教老夫找到！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_rou",
      "speaker_name": "赵柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "克星来啦……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhao_rou",
      "text": "她长得像什么，可像……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_rou",
      "speaker_name": "赵柔",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "放开我！放开我！再不放，老子骂啦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhao_rou",
      "text": "你不说清，决不放你！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "聋子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "对，千万不要放他！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_rou",
      "speaker_name": "赵柔",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "完了！完了！大哥，你们快来救我！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_zhao_rou",
      "text": "七弟放心！无论如何咱们兄弟不会让你吃亏！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_fen",
      "speaker_name": "吴愤",
      "listener": "char_long_zi",
      "text": "谁敢对你不利，咱们跟他拼了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "聋子",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "你们还敢维护？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_long_zi",
      "text": "他是咱们兄弟，当然要维护。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "聋子",
      "listener": "char_ya_zi",
      "text": "哑老，他们说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "聋子",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "这种兄弟趁早杀了，有什么可维护的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_long_zi",
      "text": "江湖所称七情魔，生死相共，你要杀他，就将咱们全杀了，否则莫想杀他。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "聋子",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "你们以为老夫就不敢将你们全杀了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_fen",
      "speaker_name": "吴愤",
      "listener": "char_long_zi",
      "text": "聋子，你有本领来杀！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bei",
      "speaker_name": "莫悲",
      "listener": "char_long_zi",
      "text": "莫要杀不着咱们，倒将有限的残生报销了！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_han",
      "speaker_name": "钟寒",
      "listener": "char_long_zi",
      "text": "咱们决不怕两个残废。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "聋子",
      "listener": "char_zhong_han",
      "text": "不怕就来打，看老夫的残生会不会就此完了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_long_zi",
      "text": "老先生何必动怒，凡事皆好善休，不一定要动干戈。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "聋子",
      "listener": "char_wen_xiao",
      "text": "别的事可善罢，惟有此事不可善罢！赵柔罪大恶极，老夫从中原追到这里，非杀不可！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "温笑",
      "listener": "char_long_zi",
      "text": "当真要杀？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    }
